---
title: Red Wine Beef & Mushroom Ragu Lasagne  with Wholemeal Garlic Bread & Radish Salad
description: This all-time-favourite pasta dish has just received a major upgrade! Beef and mushrooms are cooked in an indulgent red wine ragu, layered with a creamy cheesy sauce and fresh lasagne sheets. This hearty meal is destined to be a fan-favourite.
